sentence: what is the round trip fare from detroit to washington d c
sq2:
SELECT DISTINCT  v0.round_trip_cost, '"'||v1.fare_id||'"', '"'||v2.flight_id||'"',
 '"'||v3.airport_code||'"', '"'||v4.city_code||'"',
 '"'||v4.city_name||'"', '"'||v5.airport_code||'"',
 '"'||v6.city_code||'"', '"'||v6.city_name||'"', '"'||v7.state_code||'"' FROM fare v0,
 flight_fare v1, flight v2, airport_service v3,
 city v4, airport_service v5, city v6, state v7 
WHERE ((v0.round_trip_cost IS NOT NULL) AND ((v0.fare_id = ANY v1.fare_id) 
AND ((v1.flight_id = ANY v2.flight_id) 
AND (((v2.from_airport = ANY v3.airport_code) AND ((v3.city_code = ANY v4.city_code) 
AND (v4.city_name = 'DETROIT'))) AND ((v2.to_airport = ANY v5.airport_code) 
AND ((v5.city_code = ANY v6.city_code) 
AND ((v6.city_name = 'WASHINGTON') AND ((v6.state_code = ANY v7.state_code) 
AND (v7.state_code = 'DC')))))))));
